p://anti-lsd.blogspot.com/2010/11/blog-post_26.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘩幾撚靚仔！教徒出撚曬精前液，拮起個屎忽等太子屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-3mTK0L7WWr8/TZnGH5e31hI/AAAAAAAAAGw/bQBQYtE3P0Y/s1600/next1079_wym_002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-3mTK0L7WWr8%2FTZnGH5e31hI%2FAAAAAAAAAGw%2FbQBQYtE3P0Y%2Fs1600%2Fnext1079_wym_002.jpg&h=9269cbdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n04年，黃特漢（紅圈）因毒品案被警方拘捕，後得李柱銘之助，成功推翻販毒的認罪答辯，而被判感化十五個月。<br />\n<br />\n咪話？李柱銘？賣港入中聯辦個個民主黨個創黨主席？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-cmRLTs5eiKI/TZnGRAKVTmI/AAAAAAAAAHQ/pe-97tODa9M/s1600/next1079_wym_008.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-cmRLTs5eiKI%2FTZnGRAKVTmI%2FAAAAAAAAAHQ%2Fpe-97tODa9M%2Fs1600%2Fnext1079_wym_008.jpg&h=b09ed6ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0978f3b4917a40e70d79f14ee8e284d4f75c694","tid":1252704,"uid":121546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:26:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日野餐係口罩上面寫+852 抗議黑警冇number</span></span>"},{"pid":"cd6791d1f770de06fe6fb4f017e90d4d213fa4f5","tid":1252704,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQXj8Ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQXj8Ad.jpg&h=cd49b3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家經歷過這兩星期的抗爭運動都辛苦了! 雖然「五大訴求」(包括埋「林鄭下台」)仍然未達到，但希望大家趁呢兩日先好好地休息，之後重新裝備再齊齊繼續抗爭吧~<br />\n<br />\n不過，有啲事就真係比較急嘅，就係 - <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">距離今屆新選民登記嘅截止日期<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>仲剩番10日咋</strong></span>!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你自己、兄弟姐妹、同事朋友等等仲未登記嘅，請好好把握今次嘅機會立即登記，以便喺<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">今年24/11嘅區議會選舉</span></ins></span> 同 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: pink;\">出年立法會選舉</span></ins></strong></span>，將一個一個賣港又冇立場嘅親共政棍跟尾狗狠狠地踢出議會，將議會嘅否決權還番俾人民吧!!!<br />\n(可惜嘅係，已登記選民嘅更改資料期限已經喺2/6結束了，但大家仍需要覆查自己嘅選民資料有冇俾人更改／刪除咗，尤其係最近換咗新身分證嘅朋友)<br />\n<br />\n有關選民登記嘅資料如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">《地方選區選民》</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=f94b93cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">《功能界別選民及／或選舉委員會界別分組選民》</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=98ddd4dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">網上更新電郵地址</span></strong> - <a href=\"https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/mainEM.jsp&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk%2Fosp%2Fra008%2FmainEM.jsp%E2%80%A6&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=301c7c21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/mainEM.jsp&hellip;</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">選民資料網上查閱系統</span></span></strong> - <a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=e3775ce6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n此外，資料組嘅朋友可以好好地利用呢段時間，儲齊呢段時間來班建制狗所做嘅「好人好事」並作出整理，成為「彈藥」以供文宣組嘅朋友製作長輩圖及其他文案等，對一眾被利用嘅中年／老人家作出「反洗腦」宣傳，辛苦大家了！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>＊＊＊ <span style=\"color: pink;\">齊心登記</span>，<span style=\"color: pink;\">一齊投票</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">用選票拆散保皇狗</span> ＊＊＊</strong></span>"}]}